Sean Stone, the son of U.S. film
director  Oliver Stone , has converted to Islam while in  Iran , the
 Tehran Times  newspaper reported.  The ceremony of conversion to Shia Islam was held in the
office of a cleric in Isfahan, the newspaper said, without
giving details.  Stone, whose new Muslim name is Ali, traveled to Iran this
month to attend a film festival, according to the report. He
visited the country in September for the purposes of a
documentary, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladane Nasseri in Dubai at 
